Rebel built-in functions tests:

1. There are more than 370 built-in functions in Rebel.
2. In the beginning, create at least 3 tests for each function.
3. Many functions are overloaded, so in reality there are more
   than 532 functions to test.
4. Use mk-test-fs to create a sample directory/file tree to test
   filesystem and file functions.
5. Always use .template file
6. Running tests:
   5.1. Run a single test file:
        rebel testfile.test.rbl
   5.2. Run all test files:
        rebel *.test.rbl
